    CONSOLE
    INSTRUCTIONS


    <color=yellow>Mouse 1</color> to disable input of body <color=red>ESC</color>
    to re-enable it.


    Hold the book in hand to use it.


    INVENTORY INSTRUCTIONS


    from
    1,2,3,4.... to 9,0 you have slots. you may switch items with them'
