    m_HorizontalOverflow: 0
    m_VerticalOverflow: 1
    m_LineSpacing: 1
  m_Text: 'INSTUCTION GUIDE FOR DUMMIES


    <color=yellow>W/A/S/D</color> FOR MOVEMENT

    <color=yellow>Mouse
    1</color> (M1) for firing.

    <color=yellow>Mouse 2</color> (M2) for aiming
    or configuring

    <color=yellow>E</color> for interacting

    <color=yellow>R</color>
    for freeing your mouse


    Zero (<color=yellow>0</color>) button has wizard
    book which you can use with <color=yellow>Mouse 1</color> and stop with Escape
    (<color=red>ESC</color>) button


    One (<color=yellow>1</color>) has Tool
    Luger (similar to tool gun but its not)


    read texts to absorb information
    which you can use it later just like in real life!'
